## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Local Development

To make changes locally and test them, install the package in "editable" mode:

```bash
pip install -e .
```

This allows you to make changes without reinstalling every time.

### Testing

We use **pytest** for testing. To run the tests, simply use:

```bash
pytest
```

